query:
SELECT 
  s.name as service_name,
  a.id as api_id,
  a.name as api_name,
  p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
INNER JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
INNER JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.name IN ('WhatsApp', 'Telegram', 'Instagram', 'Facebook', 'Google,youtube,Gmail')
  AND p.countryId = 1
  AND a.active = 1
ORDER BY s.name, a.id ASC;
